    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. it's a good start. i think my students will also need to address the more controversial aspects of this stance, like the idea that strict enforcement is a moral necessity for preserving national identity. can you dig a bit deeper into the philosophical arguments there? like how proponents justify the tension between strict enforcement and humanitarian concerns?",
